creature in panic mode, and may keep burning for a short
time.
@item cold
Some cold spells and effects may slow down a creature.
@item lightning
Lightning is not very special, although acid and poison is
more common, it is less common than fire and cold, and it
usally inflicts grater damage.
@item acid
Similar to poison, but it cannot be neutralised or slowed
with poison neutralisation and slowing magic. It usally
last for a much shorter peroid.
@item poison
See @ref{Effects of poison}.
