@node Turns and rounds
@section Turns and rounds
@cindex turn
@cindex round

A turn consists of ten rounds. The notation of rounds are
merely to simply the thinking of how time passes. One round
corresponds to ten minutes in the game, hence one turn
corresponds to one minute in the game.

None attack attack often take one round or one turn, while
attack actions takes from one turn to one round. Removing
the armour, putting on a armour, digging in the backpack
all take one round. Many special abilities takes one turn.



