pressing @kbd{enter} when the line is empty will have the
same effect. Otherwise @kbd{enter} will continue to the
next action if the input is valid, or, if the input is
invalid, list valid inputs.

If you are prompted for a file, you can drag and drop a file
input your terminal emulator and press enter, as long as
your terminal emulator handles file drag and drop in the
standard way --- quoted with single quotes and with a
